                      ],
                      "text": "Relationships",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7088,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/12/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_1107416649457146883.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Война Архонтов",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Baal and Beelzebul won the Archon War together. For all the Inazumans there was only one Archon, Baal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7089,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/12/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_1090730713764694732.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Катаклизм в Каэнри'ах",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "During the Cataclysm, Makoto didn't tell her sister and went to",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4811,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/11/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_705904275694017757.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Каэнри'ах",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "alone. She wasn't a good warrior so she died.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7470,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Вельзевул",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ei is Makoto's twin sister. During Makoto's reign, she was her kagemusha. When Ei found her sister in Khaenri'ah, it was too late. They could say goodbye in Makoto's subconsciousness but Ei didn't find out why her sister left alone.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4898,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/08/237301566/513d51e0ebfd54f5da34a9f85dfaf61f_7035409058896426137.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Астарот",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Presumably, after the Cataclysm, Istaroth helped Makoto plant the Sacred Sakura in the past. For everyone in Inazuma except Ei, it seemed as if the sakura had always been there.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7498,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Кицунэ Сайгу",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7499,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Сасаюри",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7500,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Микоси Тиё",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
